title: Worst Date Wednesday: She Dropped the 15 Month Old Off and Left
description: Megan tells us a story about a guy she was hanging out with who ended up getting violently sick overnight and she heard all the noises coming out of the bathroom.  The worst part is what happened the next morning when his baby mama showed up.
